{"tid":2516831,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE娜璉意外曝光美女媽「基因超強」高顏值神複製","createTime":"2021-05-05T02:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T15:14:50.000Z","uid":222155,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e3271572508d0b01e11c1a564cee80ac1e1d1e65","tid":2516831,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2021/05/03/phpOY3lXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2FphpOY3lXa.jpg&h=8340f85c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">南韓人氣女團TWICE成員娜璉日前在官方Youtube頻道公開日常Vlog。（翻攝自twicetagram IG）</span><br />\n<br />\n南韓人氣女團TWICE成員娜璉外型可愛甜美，一直是隊內的人氣成員。日前官方Youtube頻道陸續公開了成員的日常Vlog，娜璉在影片中意外曝光媽媽的超強美貌，母女倆紅色洋裝、花朵頭飾及招牌陽光笑容100%完美複製，網友驚呼：「家族基因超強。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2021/05/03/phpPRHPmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2FphpPRHPmC.jpg&h=119c780a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">娜璉在影片中意外曝出媽媽年輕照片，母女穿著類似紅色洋裝、花朵頭飾。（翻攝自TWICE Youtube）</span><br />\n<br />\n影片是由娜璉親自拍攝，在片中她開心分享房間裡最喜歡的東西，並公開了媽媽送給她的卡片，眼尖網友也發現卡片上的她根本是媽媽的翻版，左邊是歌曲「Dance The Night Away」中的娜璉，右邊是年輕的娜璉媽媽，兩人身穿十分類似的碎花紅洋裝，陽光甜美笑容如出一轍。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/CZF9rOURmSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCZF9rOURmSM&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=04bc9459\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CZF9rOURmSM</a><br />\n6:19開始</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2021/05/03/phpRxB78n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2FphpRxB78n.jpg&h=08e4caeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">年輕娜璉媽媽與女兒外貌非常相像。（翻攝自韓網）</span><br />\n<br />\n網友紛紛留言表示：「娜璉和她媽媽幾乎長得一樣」、「還以為娜璉媽媽那張照片就是娜璉」、「真的是基因的力量」。娜璉所屬女團TWICE日前也宣布 6月將回歸歌壇，讓粉絲期待表示：「錢包已經準備好了。」"},{"pid":"8ab54c586a1a4ee4ef9b29fba2a3d7acabba0d4d","tid":2516831,"uid":222155,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手睇上面條YouTube 片幫手刷view<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c874aa48e13e686109c4862812c6a430047096d3","tid":2516831,"uid":222155,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:21:13.000Z","msg":"原來我未來外母後生嗰陣都幾正式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755655900257c6d7049f9e94b4b6ac9814ee149b","tid":2516831,"uid":300542,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"陰功畀自己老母處刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399d89e85d8f4ae024a21558f29f740f0f41c1db","tid":2516831,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af084aa5a5e897e7c59b6fcd72ae9e3000e4f70","tid":2516831,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"我璉老母揸馬莎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有我璉係咪單親，好似冇提過佢老豆"},{"pid":"64f94c294d280ff5f1c64bbfb92136f681952883","tid":2516831,"uid":46678,"like":1,"dis